    "name": "SolForge Fusion",
    "steam_appid": 2400960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SolForge Fusion is a one-of-a-kind collectible card battler where every card you play levels up, evolving into stronger forms and unlocking devastating combos as the battle unfolds. Play solo or head-to-head in tactical, ever-shifting matches where your strategy evolves with every turn. Created by Richard Garfield (<i>Magic: The Gathering</i>) and Justin Gary (<i>Ascension Deckbuilding Game</i>), SolForge Fusion fuses deep strategy with limitless variety. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FUSE DECKS TO FORGE YOUR DESTINY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/b676bb8d29bfd79037092eddde97a86f.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/b676bb8d29bfd79037092eddde97a86f.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/b676bb8d29bfd79037092eddde97a86f.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are one of the mighty Forgeborn, wielding powerful spells and commanding evolving creatures born from the fusion of two unique faction decks. Go head-to-head against players around the world, train in one-off solo matches, or explore our rich, rogue-lite campaign mode.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL UP AS YOU PLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/107fbe893125d04c69409f06147a8415.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/107fbe893125d04c69409f06147a8415.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/107fbe893125d04c69409f06147a8415.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards in SolForge Fusion don't just enter the field—they grow stronger every time you play them. Choose wisely when playing your cards, adapt your tactics, level up your creatures and spells, and outsmart your opponents in a game where timing is everything.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVERY DECK IS ONE-OF-A-KIND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/478532639ac5fd9849023daf5fed8225.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/478532639ac5fd9849023daf5fed8225.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/478532639ac5fd9849023daf5fed8225.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With more deck combinations than atoms in the universe, no two players will ever have the same deck. Combine two faction decks to forge a new strategy, and evolve your cards mid-game to unleash devastating combos.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EARN REWARDS WORTH FIGHTING FOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/4f3d3f2db3133bf85851f1081e17ef0e.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/4f3d3f2db3133bf85851f1081e17ef0e.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/4f3d3f2db3133bf85851f1081e17ef0e.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win battles and complete daily and weekly quests to unlock rewards, enhance your collection, earn distinct cosmetics, and discover new deck combinations. With both a persistent progression track and rotating seasonal achievements, your next reward is only a few games away.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLIMB THE RANKS. CLAIM THE GLORY.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/aba7fd4b2fcb39331a309e33f0cd47d5.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/aba7fd4b2fcb39331a309e33f0cd47d5.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/aba7fd4b2fcb39331a309e33f0cd47d5.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your deck to the next level in physical and digital events, seasonal leagues, and community-run tournaments. With official support for organized play and a thriving Discord community, there’s always a new challenge (and a new rival) to face.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOVE THE STORY, LIVE THE STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/085ac4d9a68ff2fe1d6c639b20a30186.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/085ac4d9a68ff2fe1d6c639b20a30186.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/085ac4d9a68ff2fe1d6c639b20a30186.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the world of Solis and participate in our one-of-a-kind Storyline events to leave your mark on SolForge forever. Our player-driven narrative evolves with the choices you make. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >READY TO PLAY. EASY TO LEARN. HARD TO MASTER.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/da80209517a6e12a7dbf30ba6ef12709.poster.avif?t=1753197505\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/da80209517a6e12a7dbf30ba6ef12709.webm?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400960/extras/da80209517a6e12a7dbf30ba6ef12709.mp4?t=1753197505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SolForge Fusion features a fully voiced tutorial to get you into the action fast. From there, dive into fast-paced battles, endlessly unique decks, and deep progression that rewards experimentation, skill, and smart deck fusions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>",
